<section id="buttonGroups">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Button groups</h1>
  </div>

  <h2>Examples</h2>
  <p>Two basic options, along with two more specific variations.</p>

  <h3>Single button group</h3>
  <p>Wrap a series of buttons with <code>.btn</code> in <code>.btn-group</code>.</p>
  <div class="bs-docs-example">
    <div class="btn-group" style="margin: 9px 0 5px;">
      <button class="btn">Left</button>
      <button class="btn">Middle</button>
      <button class="btn">Right</button>
    </div>
  </div>

<div class="tab-content">
<pre class="prettyprint linenums tab-pane fade in active" id="single-button-group-haml">
.btn-group
  %button.btn 1
  %button.btn 2
  %button.btn 3
</pre>
<pre class="prettyprint linenums tab-pane fade" id="single-button-group-html">
&lt;div class="btn-group"&gt;
&lt;button class="btn"&gt;1&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;button class="btn"&gt;2&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;button class="btn"&gt;3&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</pre>
</div>
<ul class="nav nav-pills example-types">
  <li class="active"><a href="#single-button-group-haml" data-toggle="tab">HAML</a></li>
  <li><a href="#single-button-group-html" data-toggle="tab">HTML</a></li>
</ul>

  <h3>Multiple button groups</h3>
  <p>Combine sets of <code>&lt;div class="btn-group"&gt;</code> into a <code>&lt;div class="btn-toolbar"&gt;</code> for more complex components.</p>
  <div class="bs-docs-example">
    <div class="btn-toolbar" style="margin: 0;">
      <div class="btn-group">
        <button class="btn">1</button>
        <button class="btn">2</button>
        <button class="btn">3</button>
        <button class="btn">4</button>
      </div>
      <div class="btn-group">
        <button class="btn">5</button>
        <button class="btn">6</button>
        <button class="btn">7</button>
      </div>
      <div class="btn-group">
        <button class="btn">8</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

<div class="tab-content">
<pre class="prettyprint linenums tab-pane fade in active" id="multiple-button-groups-haml">
.btn-toolbar
  .btn-group
    Lorem
</pre>
<pre class="prettyprint linenums tab-pane fade" id="multiple-button-groups-html">
&lt;div class="btn-toolbar"&gt;
&lt;div class="btn-group"&gt;
Lorem
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</pre>
</div>
<ul class="nav nav-pills example-types">
  <li class="active"><a href="#multiple-button-groups-haml" data-toggle="tab">HAML</a></li>
  <li><a href="#multiple-button-groups-html" data-toggle="tab">HTML</a></li>
</ul>

  <h3>Vertical button groups</h3>
  <p>Make a set of buttons appear vertically stacked rather than horizontally.</p>
  <div class="bs-docs-example">
    <div class="btn-group btn-group-vertical">
      <button type="button" class="btn"><i class="icon-align-left"></i></button>
      <button type="button" class="btn"><i class="icon-align-center"></i></button>
      <button type="button" class="btn"><i class="icon-align-right"></i></button>
      <button type="button" class="btn"><i class="icon-align-justify"></i></button>
    </div>
  </div>

<div class="tab-content">
<pre class="prettyprint linenums tab-pane fade in active" id="vertical-button-groups-haml">
.btn-group.btn-group-vertical
  Lorem
</pre>
<pre class="prettyprint linenums tab-pane fade" id="vertical-button-groups-html">
&lt;div class="btn-group btn-group-vertical"&gt;
Lorem
&lt;/div&gt;
</pre>
</div>
<ul class="nav nav-pills example-types">
